*.pem
*.key
*.crt
certs/

# Documentation / repo-only files
README.md
LICENSE
docs/
Docs/
**/docs/
**/Docs/
documentation.md
**/*.md

# Logs, test output, coverage, temp files
Logs/
**/Logs/
logs/
**/logs/
TestResults/
**/TestResults/
coverage/
**/coverage/
.nyc_output/
**/.nyc_output/
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp
tmp/
temp/
**/tmp/
**/temp/

