**/yarn-error.log*

# Python artifacts and local virtualenvs
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd

# Simulation/model artifacts: mounted at runtime, never baked into images
simulation-engine/gpt2-football-finetuned*/
